description: The user stabs the foe with a sharpened stone. It has a high critical-hit ratio
The user heightens its mental focus and unleashes its power. It may also lower the target's Sp. Def
The user snares the foe with grass and trips it. The heavier the foe, the greater the damage.
The user vibrates its wings to generate a damaging sound wave. It may also lower the foe's Sp. Def stat.
The user fires a beam of steel that it collected from its entire body. This also damages the user.
The user attacks the target by controlling the target's item. The move fails if the target doesn't have an item.
The user attacks everything around it and faints upon using this move. This move's power is increased on Misty Terrain.
The user electrifies its body and drops onto the target to inflict damage. If this move misses, the user takes damage instead.
The user attacks and captures opposing Pokémon using an electric net. This lowers their Speed stat.
A consecutive three-kick attack that becomes more powerful with each successful hit.
It swamps the area around the user with a giant sludge wave. It may also poison those hit.
The user throws scorching sand at the target to attack. This may also leave the target with a burn
The user gathers energy from space and boosts its Sp. Atk stat on the first turn, then attacks on the next turn.
The user attacks the target's throat, and the resultant suffering prevents the target from using moves that emit sound for two turns
The user properly coaches its ally Pokémon, boosting their Attack and Defense stats.
Spurred by desperation, the user attacks the target. This move's power is doubled if the user's previous move failed.
The user slams the target with its wings. The target is hit twice in a row
The user attacks with energy from jealousy. This leaves all opposing Pokémon that have had their stats boosted during the turn with a burn
The user fiercely attacks the target using its entire body.
The user bites the foe. If the foe is holding a Berry, the user eats it and gains its effect.
The user makes a lunge at the target, attacking with full force. This also lowers the target's Attack stat.
The user fights the foe in close without guarding itself. It also cuts the user's Defense and Sp. Def.
Crunches with sharp fangs. May lower Sp. Def.
Waggles a finger to use any Pokémon move at random.
The user yells as if it is ranting about something, making the target's Sp. Atk stat decrease.
Letting out a charming cry, the user does emotional damage to opposing Pokémon. This attack never misses.
The user steals the target's energy with a kiss. The user's HP is restored by over half of the damage taken by the target.
The user is roused, and its Attack and Sp. Atk stats increase.
The user stomps down on the ground and attacks everything in the area. Hit Pokémon's Speed stat is reduced.
The user lands and rests its body. It restores the user's HP by up to half of its max HP.
Sharply increases the user's Speed.
Charms the foe and sharply reduces its Attack.
The user attacks suddenly as if leaping out from tall grass. The user's nimble footwork boosts its Speed stat.ù
The user attacks the target by showering it with water that's so cold it saps the target's power. This also lowers the target's Attack stat.
The user shoots filthy garbage at the foe to attack. It may also poison the target.
The target is stabbed with a tentacle or arm steeped in poison. It may also poison the target.
The user focuses its willpower to its head and rams the foe. It may also make the target flinch.
After making its attack, the user rushes back to switch places with a party Pokémon in waiting.
After making its attack, the user rushes back to switch places with a party Pokémon in waiting.
